# ⭐ About

This project was created as part of my journey into **Data Analytics** and **Business Intelligence**, combining my passion for football with data-driven storytelling.

As an Argentina supporter and a long-time admirer of Lionel Messi, it was especially rewarding to see the analysis reflect Argentina's impressive tournament performance and Messi's impact among the competition's top attacking contributors.

If you found this project interesting, feel free to ⭐ the repository!
